Some notes about slurm


* LUA plugins
  Lua plugins are configured via:
** slurm.conf: 
   #+begin_example
   # JOB SUBMIT
   JobSubmitPlugins=lua
   #+end_example


** job_submit.lua:
   Here Slurm is instructed to look for all other lua plugins
   #+begin_example
   package.path = ';/share/apps/admins/slurm-lua/?.lua;' .. package.path  
   #+end_example




